Global Parking and Curbside Management Market Insights
Parking and Curbside Management Market size was valued at USD 5.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 11.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Parking and Curbside Management Market Overview
The global Parking and Curbside Management Market was valued at approximately USD 3.5 billion in 2024, and it is projected to grow at a CAGR of 11.2% over the forecast period (2024-2032). The market growth is largely driven by the increasing demand for smart parking solutions and the rising need for effective curbside management in urban areas. As cities face congestion and inefficiency in managing limited parking and curbside spaces, innovative technologies such as IoT-based solutions and real-time data analytics are being widely adopted. The market is anticipated to reach a valuation of USD 10.1 billion by 2032.

